PN,44401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FA man has been remanded in custody
OL,8,Fafter appearing in court charged in
OL,9,Frelation to a series of driving
OL,10,Fincidents that saw a police officer
OL,11,Fstruck by a stolen PSNI car.
OL,13,FThe officer sustained what police
OL,14,Fdescribed as serious injuries
OL,15,Ffollowing the collision in Downpatrick
OL,16,Fat the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe court appearance came as Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer condemned
OL,9,Fwhat he described as a "horrific
OL,10,Fincident" and said his thoughts were
OL,11,Fwith the officer injured by the stolen
OL,12,Fpolice car.
OL,14,FKieran Turley, 27, from Vianstown Road
OL,15,Fin Downpatrick, appeared before the
OL,16,Ftown's magistrates' court on Monday
OL,17,Fcharged with dangerous driving,
OL,18,Fdriving while disqualified and using a
OL,19,Fmotor vehicle with no insurance.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FDistrict judge Peter Magill refused
OL,8,Fhis application for bail and he was
OL,9,Fremanded in custody to appear before
OL,10,Fcourt again later in June.
OL,12,FPrior to his appearance in court,
OL,13,Fpolice had bailed Turley in respect of
OL,14,Ftwo other alleged offences ` driving
OL,15,Fwhilst unfit and aggravated vehicle
OL,16,Ftaking causing injury ` to allow more
OL,17,Ftime for officers to investigate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FWhile in police custody he had also
OL,8,Fbeen questioned about the attempted
OL,9,Fmurder of the police officer and
OL,10,Fseveral other driving offences.
OL,11,FHowever, he was released
OL,12,Funconditionally in respect of those
OL,13,Fspecific offences.
OL,15,FPolice subsequently arrested another
OL,16,Fman on suspicion of the attempted
OL,17,Fmurder of the officer. The 36-year-old
OL,18,Fremained in police custody on Monday
OL,19,Fbeing questioning in relation to
OL,20,Fattempted murder and aggravated
OL,21,Fvehicle taking causing injury.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FA woman, aged 27, was also arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of dangerous driving and
OL,9,Ffailing to stop for police.
OL,11,FThe incidents unfolded in the early
OL,12,Fhours of Sunday when a blue Volkswagen
OL,13,FJetta failed to stop for officers on
OL,14,Fseveral occasions in the town.
OL,16,FThe car was later located by police in
OL,17,Fthe Ballymote Walk area and officers
OL,18,Fon foot pursued a man observed exiting
OL,19,Fthe vehicle in the direction of the
OL,20,FColmcille Road.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FAs officers involved in this chase
OL,8,Freturned to their PSNI vehicle, they
OL,9,Fobserved someone in the driver's seat.
OL,10,FPolice said the individual drove
OL,11,Ferratically and directly towards one
OL,12,Fof the officers. The officer
OL,13,Fdischarged one round from his firearm
OL,14,Fbefore he was struck by the stolen
OL,15,Fpolice car.
OL,17,FThe police vehicle was abandoned a
OL,18,Fshort time later and the suspect made
OL,19,Foff from the scene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FMonday's court hearing did not focus
OL,8,Fon the incident involving the officer
OL,9,Fbeing struck by the police vehicle and
OL,10,Frather the offences linked to the
OL,11,Fdriving of the Jetta car that
OL,12,Finitiated the initial police pursuit.
OL,14,FTurley spoke briefly at the outset of
OL,15,Fthe hearing to confirm he understood
OL,16,Fthe charges he faced.
OL,18,FA PSNI detective constable told the
OL,19,Fcourt he could connect the accused to
OL,20,Fthe charges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe court heard that the Jetta failed
OL,8,Fto stop for officers on a number of
OL,9,Foccasions in Downpatrick in the early
OL,10,Fhours of Sunday, the first at around
OL,11,F4.45am.
OL,13,FOn one occasion, the vehicle did stop
OL,14,Fand a rear seat passenger exited and
OL,15,Fthrew a bottle at police.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe court heard the car then took off
OL,8,Fat speed before coming to a stop
OL,9,Fagain, when a passenger, who appeared
OL,10,Fto be holding a bottle of alcohol,
OL,11,Fexited and signalled in an apparently
OL,12,Fconfrontational way for police to
OL,13,Fapproach. The car then took off again
OL,14,Fat speed.
OL,16,FJudge Magill read out the police's
OL,17,Fdescription of the vehicle's movements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,F"Police described the driving as
OL,8,Fdangerous, weaving across both lanes
OL,9,Fof traffic, hitting the grass verge,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FThe court heard that when the car was
OL,13,Ffound at 5.30am in Ballymote Walk,
OL,14,FCCTV showed that the driver was
OL,15,Fwearing a red coloured top.
OL,17,FOfficers pursued a man wearing a red
OL,18,Ftop from the scene but lost sight of
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe court was told that Turley was
OL,8,Ffound at 7.30am in the garden of a
OL,9,Fnearby property, wearing clothes
OL,10,Fsimilar to those in the CCTV images
OL,11,Fcaptured two hours earlier and with
OL,12,Fthe keys to the Jetta in his pocket.
OL,14,FAttending police said the accused
OL,15,Fexhibited "drowsy behaviour".
OL,17,FThe court heard Turley made no comment
OL,18,Fduring his police interview.
OL,26,@wD@KOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FApplying for bail, a legal
OL,8,Frepresentative for Turley highlighted
OL,9,Fthat police had already been prepared
OL,10,Fto bail his client until September in
OL,11,Frespect of the two other alleged
OL,12,Foffences they needed more time to
OL,13,Finvestigate.
OL,15,FThe lawyer also contended that no-one
OL,16,Fhad actually seen Turley driving the
OL,17,Fvehicle. He said police were also
OL,18,Finvestigating whether a female had
OL,19,Fbeen driving the Jetta.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,F"So the police aren't really sure
OL,8,Fwho's driving the vehicle," he said.
OL,10,FAsked by the judge if a female had
OL,11,Fbeen driving the car, the detective
OL,12,Fconstable said he was not in a
OL,13,Fposition to "100%" confirm but added
OL,14,Fthat officers were still investigating
OL,15,Fa "number of different offences"
OL,17,FThe officer added: "I believe there
OL,18,Fhas been mention of potentially a
OL,19,Ffemale driving the vehicle."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@[O]uD@MOUuD@RO]wD@COUwD@`O]yD@
OL,26,ATOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe detective constable said Turley
OL,8,Fwas facing charges because he had
OL,9,Fallegedly been observed exiting the
OL,10,Fdriver's door and was found in
OL,11,Fpossession of the Jetta's keys.
OL,13,FHowever, the accused's lawyer told the
OL,14,Fcourt more than one person exited via
OL,15,Fthe driver's door.
OL,17,FHe said the circumstances of the
OL,18,Fincidents remained "very confusing"
OL,19,Fand argued that Turley should be given
OL,20,Fthe "benefit of the doubt" and be
OL,21,Freleased on bail.
OL,26,@zD@TOUzD@cO]|D@EOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe judge rejected the bail
OL,8,Fapplication and remanded Turley in
OL,9,Fcustody to appear before court again
OL,10,Fon June 25.
OL,12,FOn Monday morning, the Prime Minister
OL,13,Fcommented on the incident that saw the
OL,14,Fpolice officer being struck by the
OL,15,Fstolen PSNI vehicle.
OL,17,F"Violence against police officers is
OL,18,Fwholly unacceptable and will never be
OL,19,Ftolerated," he said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780413074
OL,3,CMan in court charged in relation to
OL,4,Cincidents that saw officer hit by
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,F"My thoughts are with the officer who
OL,8,Fwas injured, his loved ones and
OL,9,Fcolleagues across the Police Service
OL,10,Fof Northern Ireland, who continue to
OL,11,Fserve with bravery in challenging
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,F"This was a horrific incident. Those
OL,15,Fwho wear the uniform do so to protect
OL,16,Fthe public and uphold the law and any
OL,17,Fattack on them is an attack on the
OL,18,Fsafety of our communities."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/16
